					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">FCEUXD <em>should</em> allow you to set breakpoints on PPU reads.  At least the option is there... does it not work or something?
<br />
<br />When adding a breakpoint, just select the "PPU mem" radio button and keep the address between $0000-$1FFF (PPU area where CHR is stored).
<br />
<br />Or... you could just set a breakpoint on $2007 reads to accomplish the same thing if that doesn't work for some reason.</div>

